 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=silverbladetheenchanter>Silverblade the Enchanter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magi Draconis</span><br>  Posts: 2147<br> <font color=#333333>(10/29/02 3:39:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7618.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excaliburthumb1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Carefull...</span><hr size=1> Apart from AoE mobs/fear and really SICK pathing, you can use pets on most raids, but like anything, it takes skill.<br>
<br>
