<br>
Now few tips on raids when ya want to use yer pet. <br>
1) I wouldn't use him on AE mobs unless its a rush fight that doesn't fear and/or you can keep immune to fear up (59+) IE Lendi the Keeper in West Wing, I wouldn't have the pet up for clearing the mobs out prehand because on the pull you'll get hit by AE he runs up early, etc. You might be able to back him off most of the time, but one early aggro and you could very well wipe the raid. Or definitely slow things down alot. <br>
<br>
2) Also learn what mobs cast an AE spell, Like AE slow, Gflux. Same rule of thumb as AE mobs but in like SSRA mobs love casting AE slow, nothing worse than the pet intercepting the 4 pull of 60s early. <br>
<br>
3) I've noticed recently that if a mob gates with a pet on it. The pet warps to him and fights him there. Now i'm not sure if it works in any situation. The only time i've seen it recently is in AR doing IV guards. The pet would warp to their spawn with them if they gated. Unsure if it was because we could see the spawn, or just a new thing. Anyway it caused alot of confusion, because i hate killing pet w/o good reason. But we ended up having too cause risk was too high. <br>
<br>
