<br>
<br>
Raids are a long series of simple steps that need to done perfectly as often as possible in order for the raid to be successfull.   Look at it this way.  A raid of people 60 works for 4 hours to get to a certain point, that 240 Man hours, 10 man days.  I think we all have to agree that pets out of sight pose an additional, unnecessary risk.  Pets in certain zones without the owner having pet hold pose an additional, unnecessary risk.  Are you ok increasing the the chance of raid wipe and wasting that much effort simply because you had to have a pet yet didn't control it or didn't excersie basic care?<br>
<br>
I'm not saying don't have pet, I have /pet hold and a pet on most raids.  I'm just saying excercise care.  Keep the pet in sight, you are responsible for knowing what your pet is doing.  The only way to do that is by seeing it.  Also, in some place you need to pass on the pet if AE is a problem or pathing is bad and you don't have pet hold.  <br>
<br>
<br>
I have to think that everyone that raids understands this.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=7618.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=7618.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7618.topic&index=16><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.threadControl?topicID=7618.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7618.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7618.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowerfrm45">User Interface<option value="themagicianstowerspells">Spells<option value="themagicianstowerequipmentandquests">Quests<option value="themagicianstowerfrm28">Equipment<option value="themagicianstowerfrm29">Magician Pets<option value="themagicianstowerfrm30">Magicia